OL,5, WH Smith, Marks & Spencer and Argos are
OL,6, among a string of companies named for  
OL,7, failing to pay the minimum wage.       
OL,9,FMore than 200 firms face penalties of  
OL,10,Fnearly #7m and must reimburse workers  
OL,11,Ffor breaches dating back over a decade.
OL,13,FWH Smith, Marks & Spencer and Argos all
OL,14,Fsaid the breaches were unintentional   
OL,15,Fand had been swiftly remedied.         
OL,17,FIt is unclear how much they paid in    
OL,18,Ffines, but the government said         
OL,19,Fpenalties amounted to up to 200% of the
OL,20,Farrears owed.                          
